Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,1050)}您另外囑咐的東西都已經買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,總之就當作是住宿費吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,魔留石？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,寶石的原石嗎
